{"tid":1013883,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[獨遊]4日3夜關西廣域Pass之旅","createTime":"2019-02-08T16:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T16:57:49.000Z","uid":184494,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d922e52956779f4d0a46617e512769a3e5b1a6a3","tid":1013883,"uid":184494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T16:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新年快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱出完篇北海道遊記冇耐，襯變返懶惰前打埋一月啱啱去完嘅關西啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼上次第一次獨遊之後覺得好回味，<br />\n因為好鍾意富士山，所以本身想黎個快閃靜岡睇富士山<br />\n後來見到因航出Fanfares 2018 final call，於是試下買唔買到機票啦，<br />\n呀點知又俾平時冇咩運嘅我買到喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 於是就變左唔去東京去大阪喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過因為快閃好多野都黎唔切Plan，所以呢次行程冇之前北海道咁精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>洗費：</strong><br />\n機票：$1843<br />\n酒店：$1713 其中一間一泊兩食<br />\n交通：JR關西廣域周遊卷$540 (呢張pass真係好抵用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 另外用左~2000yen係其他交通到<br />\n全部洗費total用左9千左右<br />\n<br />\n<strong>行程：</strong><br />\nDay 1: 凌晨機朝早到關西機場 -&gt; 京都 -&gt; 美山<br />\nDay 2: 美山 -&gt; 近江八幡堀食近江牛 -&gt; 岡山<br />\nDay 3: 後樂園+岡山城 -&gt; 倉敷 -&gt; 倉敷三井Outlet -&gt; 神戶食神戶牛<br />\nDay 4: 神戶 -&gt; 姫路城 -&gt; 梅田 -&gt; 機場<br />\n<br />\n今次因為貪心想去多幾個縣同埋想發揮張JR Pass最大效能，所以有少少走馬看花<br />\n本身仲想再癲啲Day 1去天橋立加伊根住一晚，但因為太遲Book唔到房，所以就轉左去美山<br />\n同埋上年都去過一次京阪奈良，啲大路景點都去過，<br />\n暫時去過嘅日本地方最冇好感就係大阪，所以今次除左臨走前去梅田幫朋友睇啲野之外其他時間都skip左呢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽日開始出文，希望有人睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 歡迎相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084c0700fbee650fd342ea2b9606a499d8275b66","tid":1013883,"uid":136299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T16:37:04.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6207dd598a1f49c44f7b4d248d17686390fcd3","tid":1013883,"uid":184494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"084c0700fbee650fd342ea2b9606a499d8275b66","tid":1013883,"uid":136299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T16:37:04.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T16:57:49.000Z","msg":"Thx!!<br />\n出左啲意外開多左個一模一樣嘅post<br />\n遊記打左係嗰邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}